Class RoleInstance.PublicIP

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.management.compute.models.RoleInstance.PublicIP
  • Enclosing class:
    RoleInstance

    public static class RoleInstance.PublicIP
extends java.lang.Object
    An additional public IP that will be created for the role. The public IP will be an additional IP for the role. The role continues to be addressable via the default deployment VIP.
